    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is an exceptional example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with perfectly calibrated individual throttle bodies and a robust VANOS system. The chassis is structurally flawless, with a reinforced rear subframe and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox that delivers precise engagement. Every component, from the limited-slip differential to the cooling system and rod bearings, has been maintained to an uncompromising standard. With its factory-spec suspension geometry and pristine interior, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience in a condition rarely seen outside of a private collection.",
